name: Exploration Ball III
description:
The third piece of a series about " The Exploration Ball ". This spherical entity is present in a certain amount of my artworks. Illustrating my own soul getting lost in the large worlds. Flying around the empty spaces of the universe, floating and exploring, this sphere can have a different structure inside.
